-- Brazil National Monetary Council Simplifies Bank Branch Rules
-- B y   A r n a l d o   G a l v a o
-- 2012-04-26T21:34:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-26/brazil-national-monetary-council-simplifies-bank-branch-rules.html
Brazil ’s national monetary council
approved a resolution to simplify rules governing local
branches, the bank said in a statement published today.  The head of central bank’s regulatory department, Sergio
Odilon dos Anjos, said the measure could reduce banks’ costs by
allowing them to choose the size of their local operations in
line with local demand.  To contact the reporter on this story:
